{"tid":1162523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為創辦人任正非：就算求我也不去美設5G廠","createTime":"2019-05-20T02:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T09:50:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa5418e78857598e7b9265255a5289af7d7c98b","tid":1162523,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:24:46.000Z","msg":"美中貿易戰烽火之下，川普政府大動作封殺中國電信巨頭華為，商務部16日已將華為列為出口管制的黑名單中。<br />\n<br />\n對此，任正非日前接受《日經新聞》訪問時，美國禁令對華為影響有限，預計公司營收成長會小幅放緩、略低於20%。他表示，已做好準備，因此美供應商不向華為售出晶片也「沒關係」。<br />\n<br />\n持續開發晶片降低衝擊<br />\n<br />\n任正非表示，華為將持續開發生產晶片，已減少禁令造成的生產影響，且即使高通或是美國其他供應商不向華為售出晶片，華為也沒關係。他說：「我們已經為此做好準備了」。<br />\n<br />\n此說法呼應華為旗下的海思半導體總裁何庭波，日前在公司內部信中指出，華為多年前就做過極限生存的假設，預計有一天，美國先進晶片和技術將不可獲得，而華為仍將持續為客戶服務。<br />\n<br />\n任正非批美失信 「求我設廠也不去」<br />\n<br />\n此外，任正非也展現強硬的一面，稱華為不會任由華府擺佈，不會在美國的要求之下，像是先前中興通訊一樣更換管理階層，且排除在美國境內生產5G設備的可能性，稱「就算美國要求我們在那裡製造，我們也不會過去」。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「接二連三威脅貿易夥伴的政策讓企業不敢再冒險，同時美國也將失去信譽。」<br />\n<br />\n他還排除在美國境內生產5G設備的可能性，「就算美國要求我們在那裡製造，我們也不會過去」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，華為每年採購職約為670億美元的零件，其中約有110億美元來自美國供應商。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%81%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%92%E5%9C%A8%E6%80%95-%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA-%E5%B0%B1%E7%AE%97%E6%B1%82%E6%88%91%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8E%BB%E7%BE%8E%E8%A8%AD5g%E5%BB%A0-012700349.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2580%2595-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2588%2591%25E4%25B9%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258E%25BB%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A8%25AD5g%25E5%25BB%25A0-012700349.html&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1yKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=c7ba00bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%81%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E4%B9%9F%E6%B2%92%E5%9C%A8%E6%80%95-%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA-%E5%B0%B1%E7%AE%97%E6%B1%82%E6%88%91%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8E%BB%E7%BE%8E%E8%A8%AD5g%E5%BB%A0-012700349.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6cad6f84f0396abd36f03e39b350a750be636eb","tid":1162523,"uid":2772,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"美國人求你唔好黎"},{"pid":"ed337994088fe1e5dc192ff8356f9965c3f9dd27","tid":1162523,"uid":52459,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"走住屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b8f2004074f31952b49123a1af440ef35c57db","tid":1162523,"uid":155095,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://blog-imgs-80.fc2.com/d/e/a/dearyunjae/fc2blog_20150727060802118.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80.fc2.com%2Fd%2Fe%2Fa%2Fdearyunjae%2Ffc2blog_20150727060802118.jpg&h=5c4287f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31d9bd9ce9488e0c94c96c1ef8001ce3e878f02d","tid":1162523,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:30:25.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7b49070d8638c5ab3b5e138045533ef4ec5683","tid":1162523,"uid":12015,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"柒到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地擺明係唔俾你嚟<br />\n自己喺度攞尾彩<br />\n<br />\n話返俾自己啲支那同胞聽人地求都唔去咁"},{"pid":"ab2b7804c1fa3dc150c15b8c98948c98aa37e3dc","tid":1162523,"uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"結衣求我都唔會俾碌鳩佢含呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546bc951a23ecb2cdacee794ccf15de9283b097f","tid":116